<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Its nice to give it out for free but in combat zones, MM Guk etc. you should make people pay. On busy nights you might get constant tells like "Where are you, can i have another clarity plz?" Make em pay, whats 5pp to a lvl 30, not much but for you it adds up. Spend it on jewels. When Im traveling through "safe" zones I randomly buff people for free and announce, logging in three minutes, buffs free. However I've rarely do the logging thing because newbies send tells later like, "I went there and you didnt even show, THNX A LOT".<br>
